    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The bond with your Wildfire Spirit can save you from death. If the spirit is within 120 feet of you when you are reduced to 0 Hit Points and thereby fall &amp;Reference[Unconscious apply=false], you can cause the spirit to take damage equal to its current Hit Points (no action required). You then immediately regain Hit Points equal to twice the damage your Wildfire Spirit takes, you end the &amp;Reference[Prone apply=false] condition, standing without provoking Opportunity Attacks, and both your and your Wildfire Spirit unleash fiery energy as when you summon it.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
